📜 Usage
Put all your audio files in input_audio/ (any format: mp3, wav, amr, m4a, etc).
Set your HuggingFace token in main.py.
Run your entire pipeline: python main.py
Check results in output_txt/ and output_json/.
You now have reusable, dynamic modules for scalable, robust Egyptian Arabic meeting transcription.
You can tune preprocess.py for further denoise/normalization.
Diarizer, transcriber, and output are all ready for enhancement or swapping models.
txt and json output for every meeting.
